{"tid":2224214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普京考慮親自接種俄產武漢肺炎疫苗","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:16:15.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60c624a3ae3353e1ab7a246e79e85fd2b407ec0f","tid":2224214,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"克里姆林宮發言人佩斯科夫今天（29日）表示，俄羅斯總統普丁（Vladimir Putin）正在考慮接種武漢肺炎疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯衛星通訊社報導，佩斯科夫（Dmitry Peskov）向記者表示：「普丁作為國家元首，自然要採取特別的預防措施。普丁已經表示他在考慮接種武漢肺炎疫苗，我們正等他做出決定。」<br />\n<br />\n南韓《中央日報》今天稍早也報導，普丁昨天（28日）曾與南韓總統文在寅通電話。文在寅在電話中邀請普丁在疫情得到控制後訪問南韓，普丁對此回應說：「我會在親自接種俄產疫苗後訪韓。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200929/U6SFBKQJSBB3VCZKLPJMR7ECLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200929%2FU6SFBKQJSBB3VCZKLPJMR7ECLM%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kynGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=6aa17d48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200929%2FU6SFBKQJSBB3VCZKLPJMR7ECLM%2F&h=923eb810\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200929/U6SFBKQJSBB3VCZKLPJMR7ECLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPGPzjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPGPzjw.jpg&h=99a2d423&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa93d0284e45c307b2a61ca262a5015d6d9e22d6","tid":2224214,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"扮打實打鹽水<br />\n阿水知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}